T1  - An Anatomy of the “S&P Game”: The Effects of Changing the Rules
AU  - BENEISH, MESSOD D.
AU  - WHALEY, ROBERT E.
Y1  - 1996/12/01
PY  - 1996
DA  - 1996/12/01
DO  - https://doi.org/10.1111/j.1540-6261.1996.tb05231.x
